- If a service is DISABLED for a host then try uninstalling it, that requires expanding each role so that it has an install.yaml and an uninstall.yaml
- Allow bootstrapping without Tailscale, currently we need to tailscale already active so we can bootstrap, and even we use root even though we disable log-in for it by abusing the fact that tailscale allows us to log-in as root while having root-login disabled